Package: landisbc
Type: Package
Title: British Columbia Study-Area Tools for LANDIS-II Workflows
Description: Province of British Columbia data-preparation helpers for
    'LANDIS-II' forest-landscape simulation workflows -- for example, deriving
    observed fire-severity distributions from provincial burn-severity data for
    Dynamic Fire calibration. Companion to 'landisutils' (the study-area-agnostic
    'LANDIS-II' tooling); BC-specific data sources and mappings live here so they
    can be reused across British Columbia projects.
URL: https://github.com/FOR-CAST/landisbc
BugReports: https://github.com/FOR-CAST/landisbc/issues
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
